öíØW<?php exit; ?>a:6:{s:10:"last_error";s:0:"";s:10:"last_query";s:51:"SELECT wp_posts.* FROM wp_posts WHERE ID IN (68,55)";s:11:"last_result";a:2:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:2:"55";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2016-04-29 09:03:07";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2016-04-29 09:03:07";s:12:"post_content";s:1826:"Let's be honest. I am a geek. I have a lot of tech stuff at home, and in this article I'd like to share what I use. As a web developer I use my computer every day. I am a Mac user, I've got a 27" iMac and a Macbook Pro for doing stuff when I'm travelling. I also use a Samsung external monitor. My mouse is a Roccat Kone XTD and I use the keyboard bundled with my iMac.

<img class="size-medium wp-image-65 aligncenter" src="http://myknowledge.eu/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/imac-gallery5-2015-300x230.jpeg" alt="imac-gallery5-2015" width="300" height="230" />

By the way, the mouse is really great, I definitely remommend this mouse if you are right handed. I will post a detailed review of this mouse in the future.

For speakers, recently I bought the Harman Kardon Soundsticks Wireless, and they sound amazing. I love bass, and these speakers have excellent subwoofers. And they also have a nice, futuristic look.

<img class="size-medium wp-image-64 aligncenter" src="http://myknowledge.eu/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/B008YFD5G4.HERO_LARGE-300x300.jpg" alt="B008YFD5G4.HERO_LARGE" width="300" height="300" />

In the past I experimented doing some iOS programming in Objective-C and Swift. That's why I use an iPhone and iPad. Currently I have an iPhone SE and it suits me really well, as I have small hands. Recently I also bought the Apple Watch, and it's working great so far. I love the feeling when it does the haptic feedback thing. Since then I don't have to check my phone everytime it vibrates in my pocket.

<img class="size-medium wp-image-66 aligncenter" src="http://myknowledge.eu/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/s38sg-sbbk-sel-201603-254x300.jpeg" alt="s38sg-sbbk-sel-201603" width="254" height="300" />

And that's basically it! Next time I will share what software I use, both at home and at work.";s:10:"post_title";s:18:"What tech do I use";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:18:"what-tech-do-i-use";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-05-13 07:17:49";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2016-05-13 07:17:49";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:27:"http://myknowledge.eu/?p=55";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"post";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:1;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:2:"68";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2016-05-13 09:00:06";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2016-05-13 09:00:06";s:12:"post_content";s:1431:"In the last article I mentioned that I will write what software I use. I guess now it's the time. Currently, I work as a junior web developer and tester, so primarily I will focus on the tools that we use in the company.

Let's start with PHPStorm. PHPStorm is one of the best IDEs out there, made by a company called JetBrains. I think it is a Czech company, but I'm not sure. It has almost every feature that we need, including Composer integration, version control systems like Git, SVN built in, and most importantly, a great Intellisense. The features can also be customized and added via plugins, that really helps with my overall workflow. Plugins I use are Symfony, Laravel, PHP Annotations and some related to Nette - Latte, Neon.

Next, as a localhost server we use XAMPP, and because at home I use OS X, I also use MAMP. It's the easiest way how to set up a virtual host.

To connect securely to Git server we use Putty SSH and Pageant. I personally didn't know about this type of authorization before I started working.

As a text editor I use Visual Studio Code, or Atom. Believe it or not, VS Code is really great!

For compiling Less we use WinLess. I don't like this approach, since I used to use Sass in combination with Gulp, but since the company uses Less, I must too.

Then we use standard corporate tools from Microsoft, like Outlook, Lync, this kind of stuff.

Let me know if I missed anything.";s:10:"post_title";s:29:"What software I use every day";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:29:"what-software-i-use-every-day";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-05-13 09:01:46";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2016-05-13 09:01:46";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:27:"http://myknowledge.eu/?p=68";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"post";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}}s:8:"col_info";a:23:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":13:{s:4:"name";s:2:"ID";s:7:"orgname";s:2:"ID";s:5:"table";s:8:"wp_posts";s:8:"orgtable";s:8:"wp_posts";s:3:"def";s:0:"";s:2:"db";s:10:"d127911_wp";s:7:"catalog";s:3:"def";s:10:"max_length";i:2;s:6:"length";i:20;s:9:"charsetnr";i:63;s:5:"flags";i:49699;s:4:"type";i:8;s:8:"decimals";i:0;}i:1;O:8:"stdClass":13:{s:4:"name";s:11:"post_author";s:7:"orgname";s:11:"post_author";s:5:"table";s:8:"wp_posts";s:8:"orgtable";s:8:"wp_posts";s:3:"def";s:0:"";s:2:"db";s:10:"d127911_wp";s:7:"catalog";s:3:"def";s:10:"max_length";i:1;s:6:"length";i:20;s:9:"charsetnr";i:63;s:5:"flags";i:49193;s:4:"type";i:8;s:8:"decimals";i:0;}i:2;O:8:"stdClass":13:{s:4:"name";s:9:"post_date";s:7:"orgname";s:9:"post_date";s:5:"table";s:8:"wp_posts";s:8:"orgtable";s:8:"wp_posts";s:3:"def";s:0:"";s:2:"db";s:10:"d127911_wp";s:7:"catalog";s:3:"def";s:10:"max_length";i:19;s:6:"length";i:19;s:9:"charsetnr";i:63;s:5:"flags";i:16513;s:4:"type";i:12;s:8:"decimals";i:0;}i:3;O:8:"stdClass":13:{s:4:"name";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:7:"orgname";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:5:"table";s:8:"wp_posts";s:8:"orgtable";s:8:"wp_posts";s:3:"def";s:0:"";s:2:"db";s:10:"d127911_wp";s:7:"catalog";s:3:"def";s:10:"max_length";i:19;s:6:"length";i:19;s:9:"charsetnr";i:63;s:5:"flags";i:129;s:4:"type";i:12;s:8:"decimals";i:0;}i:4;O:8:"stdClass":13:{s:4:"name";